# Power Platform CI/CD Configuration Code Owners

# Workflows - All changes require DevOps team review
/.github/workflows/ @devops-team @platform-architects

# Documentation & Architecture
/docs/ @platform-architects @tech-leads

# Solution files - Changes require solution owner review
/src/ @solution-owner @development-team
/build/ @devops-team @qa-team

# Configuration files - Require admin review
/.github/ @devops-team
/renovate.json @devops-team
*.yml @devops-team
*.yaml @devops-team

# Security & Access Control
# Require explicit approval for credential or security-related changes
**/secrets* @security-team @devops-team
**/security* @security-team
**/credentials* @security-team @devops-team

# Release & Versioning
CHANGELOG.md @release-manager @platform-architects
VERSION @devops-team @release-manager

# Default - Project maintainers
* @project-maintainers
